{"tid":21884,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾貓義工 仆街啦你","createTime":"2016-12-04T06:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T18:05:34.000Z","uid":19159,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1c08a23b74abdc451141978d37949cf8463c19e","tid":21884,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:18:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾義工。仆啦你 <br />\n知唔知好撚多人好撚有錢間屋好撚大但虐待動物好嚴重！？ <br />\n有錢人好多都見靚就要，養養下見冇咁靚就棄<br />\n我地呢d小康家庭 俾你踩到落地底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n領養隻貓就查哂家宅 <br />\n屋企有冇800呎？<br />\n有冇25歲？<br />\n份糧有冇萬五蚊？<br />\n可唔可以每日花十個鐘陪佢地？<br />\n住咩屋？村屋公屋不考慮喎<br />\n屋企有冇大閘？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老味死人仆街貓義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n以上我一樣都符合唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩最後係愛協養到 仲養到佢地肥肥白白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a8ed6d367b7241e2db5e05ea66d308ee2c57fb","tid":21884,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:20:00.000Z","msg":"月經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3168e0c4665c5f0a0973b21c80ab8103a3f171","tid":21884,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:21:03.000Z","msg":"班柒頭直頭弱撚智，格鳩硬將自己果套標準用喺其他人果度，唔跟佢果套就話你唔適合養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c833c41b488ae3fd823452455444f9a9e65fa14","tid":21884,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:26:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"858a726db0ee6fadec13abc50a40c20589ad7166","tid":21884,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:43:04.000Z","msg":"講漏左樣<br />\n有乜冬瓜豆腐，你比佢啲資料網上見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42de205ca8d335ba823809d864b14c26b59b9c9f","tid":21884,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike