又易有病又近親 佢地老母又慘 真係領養最好 領唔到就愛協 再唔得就執 執唔到就搵好breeder買/frd送</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明明公屋可以養貓 但愛協唔比公屋申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 點分好壞breeder ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最好係自已去睇，因為無人share呢啲資訊<br />\n同埋通常一，半年一胎<br />\n所以無得即買即有，要預約，有啲要等成年先有<br />\n而且會知BB爸媽係邊個，會body check<br />\n絶左育先賣比你<br />\n總知唔係收錢就俾你咁兒戲"},{"pid":"80e67a439e095b97477b8ab783bbaeb784b6839b","tid":21884,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩呀 來自好breeder唔反對，但係係無良寵店買就on9囉 好撚多大陸貓狗埸既又易有病又近親 佢地老母又慘 真係領養最好 領唔到就愛協 再唔得就執 執唔到就搵好breeder買/frd送</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明明公屋可以養貓 但愛協唔比公屋申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 點分好壞breeder ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最好係自已去睇，因為無人share呢啲資訊<br />\n同埋通常<span style=\"color: red;\">一至年半一胎</span><br />\n所以無得即買即有，要預約，有啲要等成年先有<br />\n而且會知BB爸媽係邊個，會body check<br />\n絶左育先賣比你<br />\n總知唔係收錢就俾你咁兒戲</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1423684d963be3d2260a46a7a31432551047eb9c","tid":21884,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:53:28.000Z","msg":"街邊執算啦"},{"pid":"568a620b481ac46ebb7903c7bcad7a00426de82b","tid":21884,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:14:05.000Z","msg":"所以想人道啲買寵並唔係容易<br />\n分分鐘又貴又煩同義工領養<br />\n如果純粹想養點都係領養最好<br />\n呢度啲巴絲成日都發動到技能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有心等下都唔怕啦"},{"pid":"794d9326c94ad4ebc888b6c6e535bd390431af7d","tid":21884,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾貓義工<br />\n我有齊窗網 貓用具又有<br />\n我都係比佢踩到地底泥咁<br />\n屋企環境唔夠其他家庭靚<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦<br />\n而家求你比貓我？<br />\n自己養飽佢啦<br />\nd貓b錯過曬黃金時期搵屋企都係佢地責任<br />\n<br />\n我而家三隻貓都係論壇領養帖領養番黎<br />\n養到佢地已經肥肥白白<br />\n貓義工食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05cf515682b1c365dda93b0e1cdc636527623eb","tid":21884,"uid":3876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算通過重重難關,<br />\n領養咗都俾人check足十幾年,<br />\n要一直on call, 影相,<br />\n病咗又會質疑你養唔掂...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔覺啵 係開頭幾個月開始煩我地要send相 但之後都冇理<br />\nBtw佢地就黎要絕育啦 有冇邊間手勢好啲推介<br />\n最好港島區"},{"pid":"4b62c032ddde04552e8643dd70d9806637ffb8b5","tid":21884,"uid":16710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:38:37.000Z","msg":"貓義工不嬲垃圾"},{"pid":"f5664a047d6265fe90e19f33bc172318bdc8c019","tid":21884,"uid":26938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:49:35.000Z","msg":"我家三隻都喺D好breeder度買~貓義工!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: violet;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span>有心領養都會比佢也地趕走曬～本身養開嘅都比佢地噴到一面屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a8f6155721da2044678c08e78638848e3ce814","tid":21884,"uid":46877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T23:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"625bdd9d1149f147eff964f282c790edb4f4bf0a","tid":21884,"uid":12724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:29:00.000Z","msg":"之前陪個fd由天水圍入坑口探貓 探完個耶撚貓義工覺得我地細個又覺得我地唔識養 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （利申個陣我已經執左隻貓養左年幾 我朋友都好愛貓）之後有其他人都想領養我地睇個隻貓 個耶撚義工就成撚日唔應我地whatsapp又推三推四 搞到我朋友最後放棄去左買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知過左成個月個耶撚話另個人唔想領養啦問我地仲要唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我fd即刻block柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母啊耶撚義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw我朋友後來係fb睇到有人唔要貓 佢即刻狗衝要左 宜家組左個幸福大家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a15c63a7b18fb1e07ef701370d2ea86d54a5b13","tid":21884,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:32:33.000Z","msg":"爛口個D 抵你冇得養架WOR 格衰唔方養得掂啦~"},{"pid":"0d80f6c6a1f4d036e181982e84e156189b3e0943","tid":21884,"uid":12724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爛口個D 抵你冇得養架WOR 格衰唔方養得掂啦~</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個格都同貓義工無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23758c897c96460b45af87472cc8e6ac9b1fea2","tid":21884,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:42:35.000Z","msg":"認真講貓義係好仆街 但係我覺得有好多方法領養既 唔一定要買 當然你要買 我都冇得講乜 做好自己就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6b2fcb8da7aad94b0833bd5cdd9a6f775ba603","tid":21884,"uid":30814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:54:44.000Z","msg":"中到仆街<br />\n我都係咁覺得 之前買左隻 而加想領養多隻<br />\n但一問d義工 一係佢話遲d覆 覆極都未撚覆到<br />\n一係就講野有刺 我又唔係無錢買 我只係想幫下有需要既動物 同埋知道養殖場好唔人道 所以先領養<br />\n一問佢意見或者有咩介紹 都比人屌到一面屁 佢老母正趕客臭西"},{"pid":"57766387ccaf142717b61d814c0459f95887b185","tid":21884,"uid":2059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"其實住公屋真係唔洗諗領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要搵隻合眼緣既貓去畀你領養<br />\n你估咁易咩<br />\n唔好同我講咩愛貓就要愛晒所有貓 唔理咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁真係搵唔到咪唯有搵breeder買"},{"pid":"1c12f738faa8987bac68c14f7f1df108512abf45","tid":21884,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"點解寵物店=無良繁殖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826c834b076e27fecd48ba91b31b2a48fb425aaf","tid":21884,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"秒經"},{"pid":"20c2e0c7ab34322a4c9fe5e14d113eb58c73d5cb","tid":21884,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:12:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解寵物店=無良繁殖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGOOGLE下一大堆新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/culture/art/20130721/18342046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fculture%2Fart%2F20130721%2F18342046&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=2942f8a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fculture%2Fart%2F20130721%2F18342046&h=fc1b60c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/culture/art/20130721/18342046</a>"},{"pid":"73f043cecc2e53a2fd7066d89834c8dd2374bd94","tid":21884,"uid":25286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"買寵物都唔得，第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a2f0683964da414fbf6676ab846e20648ff7bb","tid":21884,"uid":3668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T08:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買寵物都唔得，第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾貓義工個撚個都有人格障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeaf6113dcef5c94682e9c782ee38b9d2e1934f1","tid":21884,"uid":28351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:06:42.000Z","msg":"其實真係好多貓義工真係仆街黎 好鐘意踩鳩人屋企點點點 又話你無錢 乜撚原因都有<br />\n好彩就真係之前遇到個好義工 唔會麻鳩煩煩 <br />\n住居屋都無嫌我無位養呀盛<br />\n如果有人想知個義工contact可以講聲 見佢真係好鍚貓 執埋執埋好多貓等出俾有心人真係好辛苦"},{"pid":"8e32e46cf3bccabad5b1ad77ccf32d923a137315","tid":21884,"uid":56401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>爛口個D 抵你冇得養架WOR 格衰唔方養得掂啦~</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個格都同貓義工無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢個格直頭等於宣布自己就係貓義工啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一遇撚到呢種臭閪貓義工我就開鳩佢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8efcb06c01f3fa24d3adbc230dc6dfcc688e932","tid":21884,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T18:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中到仆街<br />\n我都係咁覺得 之前買左隻 而加想領養多隻<br />\n但一問d義工 一係佢話遲d覆 覆極都未撚覆到<br />\n一係就講野有刺 我又唔係無錢買 我只係想幫下有需要既動物 同埋知道養殖場好唔人道 所以先領養<br />\n一問佢意見或者有咩介紹 都比人屌到一面屁 佢老母正趕客臭西</blockquote><br />\n愛協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db37838dc4423f315c24a9f83cad2a2e976ad655","tid":21884,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T18:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實住公屋真係唔洗諗領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要搵隻合眼緣既貓去畀你領養<br />\n你估咁易咩<br />\n唔好同我講咩愛貓就要愛晒所有貓 唔理咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁真係搵唔到咪唯有搵breeder買</blockquote><br />\n房委會轄下的公屋可以養絕咗育嘅貓, 可能佢係房協轄下的公屋就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />住房委公屋可以去愛協領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451a4d3205c1443f095d78407d3cc774e99760ef","tid":21884,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T18:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買寵物都唔得，第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好易買到有病嘅，醫藥費貴過你買返嚟嘅價"},{"pid":"991efc4c642f094e8dc2343575158aa94aac9fec","tid":21884,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T18:33:18.000Z","msg":"開名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7534b1c74249a0abf49135ff28da7e695f460cc","tid":21884,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T18:38:43.000Z","msg":"搞咩又喺度鼓吹買貓，明明又貴，近親繁殖又容易有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前咪有個post講咗有巴打住公屋都喺SPCA領養到貓囉，唔洗家訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋有巴打整咗領養app:HKAppDopt,入面有啲唔洗資產審查嘅"},{"pid":"775ac4ac260ed7d7c9be67b616e781868dcde6a5","tid":21884,"uid":51513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:52:47.000Z","msg":"可能有人鍾意名種貓呢 我話養老媽都叫我買 佢唔鍾意唐貓 咁無計嫁 養得就當家人 揀女朋友都想要靚 唔鍾意唐貓都無計嫁"},{"pid":"2d02b266fd28d147c47d87ed30fa4bd9dcfe9c09","tid":21884,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"公屋都唔比養&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;你想佢犯法咩<br />\nbtw其他野都好撚仆街"},{"pid":"2f38cf5482bc67dd4d322650128e8edad1164c67","tid":21884,"uid":53602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公屋都唔比養&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;你想佢犯法咩<br />\nbtw其他野都好撚仆街</blockquote><br />\n房委會資助房屋小組委員會於2003年9月25日，決定維持不准在公屋養狗的限制，惟容許租戶飼養不會危害健康及造成滋擾的細小家庭寵物 。其他野生/入口動物和馴養農畜一律嚴禁在公屋飼養。<br />\n<br />\n「家庭小寵物」包括時下寵物市場供應的小寵物，而且一般養在籠、展示箱、水族箱或其他特製容器內，例如貓、雀鳥 (鴿子除外)、倉鼠、龍貓、葵鼠、兔子、烏龜、水生動物等。如欲養貓的租戶，必須安排貓兒預先接受絕育手術。<br />\n<br />\n做咩啫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔睇清楚我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔信你自己睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/public-housing/estate-management/marking-scheme-for-estate-management-enforcement/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic-housing%2Festate-management%2Fmarking-scheme-for-estate-management-enforcement%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=51f05b1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/public-housing/estate-management/marking-scheme-for-estate-management-enforcement/</a>"}]}